%e A396463 The grid is as follows:
%e A396463 0  1  8  9  24 25
%e A396463 3  2  7  10 23 26
%e A396463 4  5  6  11 22 27
%e A396463 15 14 13 12 21 .
%e A396463 16 17 18 19 20 .
%e A396463 .  .  .  .  .  .
%e A396463 And gets occupied as follows:
%e A396463 K A . A . K
%e A396463 K F K K . A
%e A396463 F K . A K .
%e A396463 A . F K . A
%e A396463 . F K F A K
%e A396463 . A . F . F
%e A396463 Where the . means that the position remains unoccupied.
